  "meta": {
    "description": "Kedy salon lifecycle notifications. Hourly cron queries 8 notification types (3 reminders, no-show, survey, google maps, birthday, winback) and POSTs each row to the corresponding https://app.berkai.shop/api/internal/lifecycle/* endpoint. Backend handles context resolution, send, and NotificationLog dedup — n8n is dumb dispatch only.\n\nAPI host is hardcoded to https://app.berkai.shop in all Send nodes.\n\nRequired n8n credentials:\n- 'Kedy Postgres' (postgres): DATABASE_URL of meta backend\n- 'Kedy Internal API Key' (httpHeaderAuth): Name='x-internal-api-key', Value=$INTERNAL_API_KEY",
    "templateCredsSetupCompleted": false
  }
